Frequency: How often to trigger the event (<= 1 means EVERY time).
ParticleFrequency: Only fire the first time (collision only).
CustomName: Should the event tag with a custom name? Leave blank for the default.
ParticleModuleEventsToSendToGame: The events we want to fire off when this event has been generated
FirstTimeOnly: Only fire the first time (collision only).
LastTimeOnly: Only fire the last time (collision only).
UseReflectedImpactVector: Use the impact FVector not the hit normal (collision only).
bUseOrbitOffset: Use the orbit offset when computing the position at which the event occurred.
